high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the kitchen counter right of the oven
Pick up the spatula from the counter
Turn around and walk down to the kitchen counter by the microwave
Open the kitchen drawer under the microwave and put the spatula in it
Walk a couple feet further left past the microwave and turn to face the counter
Pick up the spatula from the counter
Move a couple feet right and turn to face the counter by the microwave
Open the kitchen drawer under the microwave and put the spatula in it
anns.task_desc: Put the spatulas in the kitchen drawer

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the spatula from the edge of the counter.
Turn and walk to the microwave on the right.
Open the drawer below the counter where the microwave is, place the spatula inside the drawer, close the drawer.
Walk to the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the spatula to the left of the microwave.
Move to the front of the microwave.
Open the drawer below the microwave, place the spatula in the drawer behind the first spatula, close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: To move two spatulas to the drawer below the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the counter, then turn right and walk to the spatula on the counter top by the toaster.
Pick up the spatula from the counter top.
Turn around and walk forward across the room to the microwave on the counter.
Open the drawer directly underneath the microwave, put the spatula in it and close the drawer.
Walk left to the spatula on the counter top to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the spatula from the counter top.
Turn right and walk back to the same drawer where you put the first spatula in.
Open that drawer and put the spatula in it, behind the first spatula, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two spatulas in a drawer.
